0- move to your kafka folder
1- Run Zookeeper using the following command: zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties
2- Run Kafka server using the following command: kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties
3- Create Topic : kafka-topics.sh --bootstrap-server <serverURL:port> --<topicname> --create
4- Run Producer : kafka-console-producer.sh --bootstrap-server <serverURL:port> --topic <topicname>
5- Run Consumer : kafka-console-consumer.sh --bootstrap-server <serverURL:port> --topic <topicname>
